ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
SortByColumns(
    If(
        gblUserRole.is_admin,
        SAP_TICKETING_DB,
        gblUserRole.is_assign,
        Filter(
            SAP_TICKETING_DB,
            gblUserO365Info.email in InitialAssignee_email || gblUserO365Info.email in AssignedTo_email
        ),
        Filter(
            SAP_TICKETING_DB,
            'User Email' = gblUserO365Info.email
        )
    ),
    "TicketStatusOrder",
    Ascending,
    "Created",
    Ascending,
    "Counter",
    Ascending,
   
)
